Corey Page https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Corey_Page 0 Corey Page (born 27 March 1975) is an Australian film and television actor. He has appeared in leading roles in the television series Heartbreak High in Australia. Additionally, he was a series regular in the US television series The City from 1995–96. Page also co-starred in the MTV/Paramount feature film, Dead Man on Campus in 1998, and supporting role in the independent film The Road Home. Most recently, Page served as on-set drama coach for the independent Australian film Newcastle, directed by US writer/director, Dan Castle and as Matthew Webster in the 2011 Australian film Wrath.
